# ----------------------------------------------------------------
# Quarto Specific
# ----------------------------------------------------------------

# The main Quarto metadata/build directory.
/_quarto/
*_quarto_files/

# Freeze directory for computational documents
/_freeze/

# Ignore all HTML, PDF, and MS Word/Office files generated by Quarto.
# Only track the source .qmd files.
*.html
*.pdf
*.docx
*.pptx
*.epub
*.odt

# If you render a website, the output directory is often `_site` or `docs`.
_site/
docs/